    <string name="byte_test_docs_title">Paste format</string>
    <string name="byte_test_docs_intro">Byte Test can read clipboard lines where a byte index is assigned a two-digit hex value.</string>
    <string name="byte_test_docs_spacing">Spaces are flexible: [0] = 02 and [0]=02 are both valid. Lowercase hex is accepted and normalized to uppercase when pasted.</string>
    <string name="byte_test_docs_name_mode">If you include a name and mode, the sequence editor will import those too. Mode can be FULL_REPORT or SERIES.</string>
    <string name="byte_test_docs_modes">In Full report mode, the listed indexes are written into their positions in one full report, while every other byte remains 00. In Series mode, the lines can be played as commands sent one after another.</string>
    <string name="byte_test_docs_error_handling">If any line is invalid, the app will not partially mix it in. Fix the format and paste again.</string>
